data.description: Nestled in the heart of downtown Statesboro, this 3 bedroom 2 bathroom completely remodeled home offers a blend of classic elegance and modern comfort.  This home boasts generously sized bedrooms and bathrooms, and large walk in closets ensuring everyone enjoys their own private retreat.   The kitchen is a chef's delight, complete with modern appliances, ample storage, and a cozy breakfast nook perfect for enjoying your morning coffee or casual meals with loved ones. Conveniently located near schools, parks, shopping, and dining, this residence offers the epitome of suburban living with urban convenience. Don't miss the opportunity to make 5 W Inman Street your new address and experience the charm and comfort this home has to offer.
